WEBVTT

01:29:01.024 --> 01:29:03.691
Listen, this kind of inferiority
complex isn't healthy.

01:29:03.858 --> 01:29:06.899
They agreed to this marriage
knowing exactly who we are.

01:29:06.941 --> 01:29:08.816
Oh, please! It's the result
of my prayers!

01:29:08.858 --> 01:29:10.108
Fine, if you say so.
